title: SpaceX Falcon heavy rocket blasts off from Florida in debut test flight
text:
SpaceX Falcon heavy rocket blasts off from Florida in debut test flight 5:02pm EST - 01:35 
A new SpaceX jumbo rocket built to be the world's most powerful launch vehicle in operation blasted off from Florida on Tuesday in its debut test launch in a milestone for Silicon Valley billionaire entrepreneur Elon Musk's rocket company.
